          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center space-y-8 p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-orange-light to-white hover:shadow-glow transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-tech-orange/10">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-orange to-tech-orange-dark rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-medium hover:animate-bounce-gentle">
