          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            We use modern development practices and proven technologies to build maintainable, secure applications that developers love to work with.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center space-y-8 p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-emerald-light to-white hover:shadow-glow transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-tech-emerald/10">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-emerald to-tech-emerald-dark rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-medium hover:animate-bounce-gentle">
            <span class="text-4xl">üìà</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Continuous Improvement</h3>
          <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            We stay current with industry best practices and continuously refine our development processes to deliver even better results.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center space-y-8 p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-pink-light to-white hover:shadow-glow transform hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 border border-tech-pink/10">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-tech-pink to-tech-pink-dark rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-medium hover:animate-bounce-gentle">
