        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Our diverse team brings together technical expertise, creative thinking, and a shared commitment to making work more joyful through technology.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center space-y-8 p-12 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-indigo/10 shadow-xl shadow-indigo/5 relative overflow-hidden">
